--- In nbwrpg@y..., "x_rauq_x" <x_rauq_x@y...> wrote:
> ooC: It's been a while since I posted with Scryed... She's uhh 
> *cough* coming back from a long patrol, ya, that's it! =p
> 
> --Scryed--
> 
> Scryed pads along casually as she moves towards the Maximal Base, 
> rather green folliage brushes against her sides, and a flock of 
> birds -- she was unfaimilar with them -- took flight as she 
> disturbed their location. Most animals didn't want to bother a 
> moderately large black bear, and Scryed didn't really want to be 
> bothrered that much. She was enjoying the peacefulness of the 
> surroundings.
> 
> "Drat," she mumbles to herself as she steps into a muddy puddle 
> which was hidden by some light brush, and that seemed to be created 
> by a small brook which was slowly filling a small pool farther down 
> the valley. <I'd better get back soon, I'm a little late for my 
> patrol report, as uneventful as it was.> Picking up her pace, the 
> bear-bot trotted along carefully and emerged from the end of the 
> valley into sight of the Maximal Base.
> 
> Moments later,
> 
> Scryed entered the base, and headed to the control room, looking 
for 
> Talos as she wasn't aware that Talos was not in charge.
